ally dangerous, don't paint them in dark colours.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/iEowcVm.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Light coloured wood with screws in is easily seen.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fENY1DR.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Waste from building sites might have screws and nails in them, don't leave them laying around where they could damage other people's vehicles.

